565
00:35:56,060 --> 00:35:57,800
How beautiful.

566
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:03,140
What's the matter?

567
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:08,700
Nothing.

568
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:10,780
I'm just glad you see this place

569
00:36:12,060 --> 00:36:14,060
as home now.

570
00:36:14,940 --> 00:36:17,100
- Let's hang them up. 
 - Okay.

571
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:18,960
- This string? 
 - Hang them there.

572
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:20,240
Okay.

573
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,280
Be careful.

574
00:36:26,500 --> 00:36:28,600
Beautiful.

575
00:36:30,460 --> 00:36:32,740
I love this kind of life.

576
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:34,100
Finally a break from hectic life.

577
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:38,140
Being able to enjoy the view and cook with loved ones.

578
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:39,860
Me, too.

579
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:45,820
Tong Tong.

580
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:49,300
I'll work hard and bring your mom here

581
00:36:49,300 --> 00:36:51,200
to live with us soon.

