00:37:11,120 --> 00:37:12,980
Fish Fillet Congee.

590
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:16,220
Be careful; it's hot.

591
00:37:16,220 --> 00:37:17,240
How is it?

592
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:18,920
Quite good.

