very delicious.

607
00:38:06,980 --> 00:38:08,787
Really?

608
00:38:08,787 --> 00:38:10,840
- Yes. 
 - Let me try it.

609
00:38:15,540 --> 00:38:17,900
Let's add some salt.

610
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:19,808
 All of it? 

